===Etymology===
After Swedish [[astronomer]] [[w:Anders Celsius|Anders Celsius]] (1701&ndash;1744), who first proposed the [[centigrade]] scale in 1742.

===Proper noun===
'''Celsius'''

#A [[metric]] [[scale]] of temperature with 0.01&deg;C as the [[triple point]] of water at [[standard atmospheric pressure]].

